{"tid":502434,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"被友人下藥　港男睡夢中遭搓鳥","createTime":"2017-12-18T01:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T15:00:30.000Z","uid":122,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4d1a11aeb926b9a0cc7a116986e99e442baa29af","tid":502434,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T01:22:57.000Z","msg":"台北市隋姓男子今年2月將樓中樓的閣樓空間，出租給香港籍男性友人，還煮泡麵、準備酒水招待港男，但實際上卻在食物中下藥，隋男隔日清晨爬上港男的床，躲在棉被裡面玩弄港男的生殖器，但因用力過猛，港男被痛醒，嚇得把隋男推開並逃離現場。雖然隋男否認犯行，但士林地檢署認為港男指證歷歷，仍依強制猥褻罪起訴隋男。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，隋男和港男是舊識，港男因妻子是台灣人，時常來台短住。今年2月11日港男再次來台探親旅遊，向隋男租借樓中樓的閣樓空間，隋男則和另名王姓友人住在一樓房間，同月12日，隋男煮泡麵、準備果乾和酒招待港男，港男不疑有他，全部吃下肚。<br />\n<br />\n未料隔日清晨，港男睡到一半，突然覺得下體疼痛，驚醒後發現棉被鼓鼓的，嚇得掀開棉被竟發現隋男，港男故作鎮定到浴室盥洗接著逃離現場，並將此事用LINE告知台灣妻子。兩人相見後，港男妻子發現丈夫眼神恍惚、步履蹣跚，懷疑他遭人下藥，趕緊帶丈夫到附近檢驗所檢查，抽血鑑定顯示港男血液中有FM2等鎮定安眠劑，兩人立刻報警。<br />\n<br />\n但隋男自始至終都不承認犯行，強調他什麼都不知道，也沒有持有安眠藥，港男當天清晨沒有說什麼話，就自行離開了，「我也不知道發生什麼事情」。<br />\n<br />\n但士林地檢署檢察官調取隋男的病歷資料，發現其有憂鬱症，會定期到醫院拿FM2安眠藥劑，且港男血液中殘留的藥物和隋男所持有的安眠藥相符，檢方因此不採信隋男辯詞，依強制猥褻罪起訴隋男。（顏凡裴／台北報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://giant.gfycat.com/FormalChubbyAntarcticgiantpetrel.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgiant.gfycat.com%2FFormalChubbyAntarcticgiantpetrel.gif&h=cfce97a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4752cc4c7f6fe8d6a702c486f1f66da8c47d94aa","tid":502434,"uid":32818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T01:26:15.000Z","msg":"達哥個friend?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad7e5d2c87f504659edc0ed777ab8762a6f82b3","tid":502434,"uid":2040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T04:05:36.000Z","msg":"gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6137aeeb812d4d879e118ffca7417c6080dcdafd","tid":502434,"uid":100012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T04:07:46.000Z","msg":"快點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遠離我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955cd9d6de3c35e58ef0a221a540d86c8fe9d27f","tid":502434,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T09:11:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4399088e935e9ce3f0ea0b9c9c4d911628953580","tid":502434,"uid":131176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T09:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf22ee13abaf7fc1dbedf5e1c1e5a31a9fa1c6e","tid":502434,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T09:17:20.000Z","msg":"想知有冇射到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20c46766a910360ad1f3a5742cc7586f3fc49bf","tid":502434,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T15:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/12-20-2017/b6pA9Q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F12-20-2017%2Fb6pA9Q.gif&h=c70afb3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張先啱"}]}